messages.title: Standing up for Vauxhall
messages.content: Stop Brexit. More and better council homes. Protect young people. Take action on climate change.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Stop selling off & knocking down our council homes, start building council homes as part of mixed communities where local people can live, rents that local people can afford

mentions.candidate: Sarah Lewis will stand up for our homes
